@lorenzfischer As you mention, this can be solved by doing a binary search on batch size.

The odd thing, and the reason for this bug, is this happening on the **second** epoch.

Usually, if one is able to complete a **single** epoch the batch selection problem is solved for the combination of GPU and data set, but an OOM on the **second** epoch indicates that this is not always the case and should be explored.

